T02TD3391E:56b-1: dvi bhu dza hi ru ka s'a dha nam /
T02TD3391E:56b-3: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i he ru ka'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3391E:56b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3391E:56b-5: grogs med dga' ba'i yid kyis ni //
T02TD3391E:56b-6: dur khrod brgyad kyi dbus gnas pa //
T02TD3391E:56b-7: shes rab thabs kyi cho ga yis //
T02TD3391E:56b-8: zla ba nyi ma rab sbyor ba //
T02TD3391E:56b-9: a'a li k'a li mnyam sbyor bas //
T02TD3391E:56b-10: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsgom par bya //
T02TD3391E:56b-11: de la h'um yig yongs su gyur //
T02TD3391E:56b-12: rdo rje rva dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD3391E:56b-13: skyil krung phyed pas ro la gnas //
T02TD3391E:56b-14: mi yi pags pa'i gos bsnams pas //
T02TD3391E:56b-15: thal bas lus la byugs pa ste //
T02TD3391E:56b-16: 'bar ba'i rdo rje g-yas pa na //
T02TD3391E:56b-17: g-yo ba'i ba dan kha tv'am ga //
T02TD3391E:56b-18: khrag ldan thod pa g-yon du'o //
T02TD3391E:56b-19: mgo bo brgya phyed phreng ba yis //
T02TD3391E:56b-20: yid du 'ong ba'i do shal dbyangs //
T02TD3391E:56b-21: cung zhig zhal gyis mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD3391E:56b-22: spyan gsum dmar po ro ldan pa //
T02TD3391E:56b-23: dbu skra kham pa gyen du 'khyil //
T02TD3391E:56b-24: mi bskyod pa yi dbu rgyan can //
T02TD3391E:56b-25: rna cha dag dang rab tu ldan //
T02TD3391E:56b-26: rus pa'i rgyan gyis mdzes pa ste //
T02TD3391E:56b-27: dbu la thod pa lnga dang ldan //
T02TD3391E:56b-28: sangs rgyas nyid bzhin bsam bya ste //
T02TD3391E:56b-29: rgas dang 'chi ba zlog byed pa'o //
T02TD3391E:56b-30: sv'a h'a phat h'um aom zhes bya ba ni mdor bsdus pa'o //
T02TD3391E:56b-31: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i he ru ka'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD3391E:56b-33: // / pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3391E:56b-34: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o //
